# Author       : Copyright (C) 2020 Richard Romig, 29 Sep 2020
# Email        : rick.romig@gmail.com
# Created      : 29 Sep 2020
# Last updated : 29 Jan 2026
# Comments     : Can sync to one or all machines on the network.
#              : LOCALNET is declared in functionlib
